Bxg5 22. fxg5 Nxe1
{ Just because you win the exchange does not mean you win the game. Black still has to take care about being mated. }
23. Bxe1 Rb8
{ Black can take the draw with  24.Qa7   24.Qxa6 ?  Rxb2  and White has no attacking threats  24...Ra8  25.Qb7  Rb8  etc.,   or play for more with the piece sacrifice  24.Qa7  Bxh3 !?  25.gxh3  Qxg5+. }
