{ We reach the traditional mainline of the Four Pawns Attack. This same position can also be reached with a King's Indian move order. White is placing all his hopes on the shock and awe tactics of the central pawn phalanx, but with deft movement Black can cut through White's offensive and neutralize the attack. }
